phrases: At that moment, the wind had suddenly blown.
Among the scattering cherry blossom petals in full bloom,
the young masked man murmured something to the cat nestling at his feet.
Amazingly, the cat had talked as if it was a natural thing to do.
Ah, amazing, the plot's developing!
And then, and then?
And then, the masked man fluttered like...
Hey, you are killing the mood!
Give me a break!
Why the heck is everyone mating?
This is why I hate spring.
I am Ootsuka Mayu.
I am a member of the 4th Foreign Affairs Department in the Police.
Just between us, I was in the manga club in my university,
and I am actually pretty into it.
The anime I am into now, is...
Maurice The Rose.
My hobby is writing stories.
Of course, I have done many doujins, and I have a lot of fans as well.
The pollen this year is terrible.
This is why I hate spring.
The masked man standing among the cherry blossom trees.
This image came to mind from a dream I had last night.
No, was it really a dream?
Even now, it is still a bit vague.
The members of the 4th unit had decided to hold a flower-watching party that night.
What is this?
It is information that the contractor who was killed was holding onto the other day.
It looks like the number for a safety deposit box and we have found out where it is, but...
The critical number is missing.
The stolen goods from the incident at the Gate.
I believe it is related.
Under a cherry blossom tree?
Yeah, it seems a contractor who had taken some goods from the Gate was buried there.
So, I have to kill that contractor?
No, your job is only to dig up the goods.
What is buried is only a sample, but
there should be a numeric password written on a memo or something.
Do not forget about it.
Is that it?
Do not let your guard down.
I have a feeling that someone may try to steal it ba-
You okay?
Shut up.
Allergic to pollen?
During times like this, I am happy that I am a cat.
I hear cats are allergic to pollen, too.
Really?
Do not worry, Mao.
Pollen will not affect us.
What?
Contractors do not see dreams and are not allergic to pollen.
That is the first time I heard that.
In the end, contractors are monsters.
There is nothing strange no matter what it may be.
Is it true?
Oh yeah, where is Yin?
That pink girl must have have come again.
Pink girl?
From the first time they met when Yin ran away, she is been going there ever since.
Here.
Was not it great?
Yeah.
I will tell you about an interesting doujin story next time, okay?
It is even more risque!
What is it called?
Moe moe?
It seems that she is become involved with a dangerous world now.
Tell her to cut her ties.
It will be problematic if she let us out information to a normal person.
Here you go, Matsumoto.
Ah, thank you.
Saitou seems a bit gloomy.
It is because the chief could not make it.
He is probably dreaming of being alone with her after watching the flowers if things go well.
He should just tell her.
The chief is pretty dense about things like that.
Well, he has to think about their positions, too.
It does not seem like spring will be coming for him.
But there are also people like you who bow down to their colleagues.
W-What silly things are you saying, Matsumoto?!
H-Here, another one.
I have had enough.
Be careful, Ootsuka, he just might be the one who is thinking about what will happen if things go well.
I will be all right, I do not really like young people.
A refined person like you, Matsumoto, is more...
Just kidding.
To be truthful...
I was not really interested in real men...
Until that time.
Like I said!
You have got to be more forward!
Kouno just disappeared somewhere after some office lady seduced him!
Geez, she is a bad drunk.
If you like her, you should tell her clearly!
Geez, you just do not understand a woman's heart!
You should research and read some novels!
Novels?
Those things?
What do you mean, those things?
You will understand when you write stories, too!
Like how delicate people's hearts are!
Oh?
You write some?
Ah, oh no, Matsumoto, you are making me embarrassed.
If you search for MayuMayu on the computer, you can read my stories right away!
Eh, are you interested?
I may not look like it, but I was once a young man who was into literature.
I have read quite a bit, like works from Kamizaki and Kajii.
Wow, you really are refined, Matsumoto!
Ah, I guess...
Beneath the cherry blossom tree lies a buried corpse.
Or some mystery like that.
Let us begin.
A buried corpse, huh?
Ah, I should not have asked something that weird.
Why do I, feared as the Black Reaper, have to do this?
This is it?
What about the numerical password?
Is there a memo or something?
No.
This is it, it is written right on it.
W-What was that?
A-A pervert!
S-S-Stay away!
This is the number.
You heard the number just now, did not you?
I-I heard nothing.
The number 4697635!
You heard it again!
N-No, it is because you said it!
Shut up!
Dammit!
I cannot keep things a secret because of my remuneration!
Remuneration?
I said something I should not have again!
I cannot let you go now because you heard things you should not have.
I-I do not remember any numbers.
See?
You do remember.
T-That is because you said it over and over!
S-Stop!
Things seemed so detached from reality just now,
and all I could remember was the appearance of the person who saved me.
He was beautiful.
Especially the line of his collarbone.
I remembered that he had danced like the air, though.
And there my memory stops.
You got her?
Tell the ones on top to erase her memory.
What is it?
Public Safety Department?
Which means she knows that contractors exist.
In that case, if we use the ME, it will not mean we have cleared out every trace.
If she is part of Public Safety, then at the very least, she will not be stupid and reveal information about us to the public.
And if she does?
If that happens, there is only one thing to do.
Take the goods to Huang, Mao.
I will take care of the rest.
I got it.
A dream?
So it was...
That is all I could believe it was.
But for some reason, my pulsing heart just would not stop.
And then...
A story began to flow from me.
It was like a drunken spring dream.
The cat had told the masked man the mysterious password.
Number, huh?
What would work?
And for some reason, this number from my dream was burned onto my mind.
Episode Twenty-Six Beneath Cherry Blossoms in Full Bloom...
You lost the goods?
Do not give me that crap!
Sorry, unexpected things happened.
Cats have it tough during this season.
I desperately looked for it, but...
Do not worry, I will find it for sure.
You better!
Damn it, everyone is so...
By the way, do not get too close to that girl, Yin.
You know what situation you are in, right?
Huang, she is made a friend, so a little bit...
Stay out of this!
You got it?
Yes.
There it is!
Hey!
It is mine!
I have been looking for this for 2 years!
The Maurice pilot is super rare!
What are you saying?
This Maurice has been waiting for me!
A book cannot possibly wait for you!
Your head's gone crazy!
What is crazy is your head!
Are you serious?
Are you really the MayuMayu who wrote Maurice's Night?
Yeah.
I cannot believe I called such a great person a brute and a swine.
If there were a hole, I would like to crawl into it right now.
It is all right, you just need to be careful from now on.
Oh yeah, that story you uploaded yesterday about the masked man was cool!
Eh?
You read it already?
It is an original character, right?
How is he going to get involved with Maurice?
Well, you will just have to wait.
It will be unfair to other fans.
I see...
But the masked man with delicious collarbones is really great!
I know someone like that, too.
Eh?
A masked man?
No, someone with nice collarbones.
Thanks for the meal.
Come again!
Those collarbones...!
See?
They are delicious, are not they?
No doubt...
There is no doubt!
W-What is wrong?
Ah, no, it is nothing.
Those are the collarbones that saved me.
No doubt about it.
It was not a dream!
It was not a dream!
A-Are you okay?
Please tell me where he lives!
No!
I am the only one allowed to stalk him!
I have been in a slump these days.
Is not that really bad?
I am sure I would be able to write something interesting if I met him.
Umitsuki Apartments
On that night, my legs had finally made their way to the Umitsuki Apartment.
My desire to meet him had overcome me.
What am I doing?
Ootsuka.
Ootsuka!
Y-Yes!
Are you so busy that you are losing sleep?
N-No!
Just what do I...
Could it be...
These feelings...
Why is she looking for us?
Could it be that she knows who we are?
You still cannot find it?
Yeah.
What the hell are you doing?
Cannot you at least remember the password?
I do remember some of it.
What did you just say, Yin?
The password.
Jun, who had received the password from the masked man,
ran full speed to the zoo where Maurice was being kept.
And then he yelled,
Maurice, I need you after all.
Yin, w-what are you saying?
Even humans and elephants can love each other.
It may be forbidden love,
but Maurice, I will live my life with that love.
Maurice's Night, this is it!
What is this?
Are you saying this number is the complete password?
I just let Kouno go and confir
Bingo!
It certainly is the right number.
But, someone else got here already.
We were too late!
Why is that number here, though?
I do not know, but I heard that it is a story she had written.
Story?
So you have read it, Matsumoto?
Yeah...
The masked man is also written here.
If it is about BK-201...
Ootsuka said that she did not see him, though.
Which means she got information from another source.
It will be dangerous if she makes any bad moves.
That is right, we have got the goods, but the information has been leaked.
They have got you tailed, too.
You know what to do, right?
Yeah.
There it is!
All right!
You lost her?
What the heck are you doing?
You are...
Ootsuka!
Get in!
Why are you here, chief?
He is a contractor?
Do you want to get killed?
Contractor?
But he is the one who save
Just hurry up!
Chief!
Idiot!
Come on!
What is going on?
It is BK-201, the Black Reaper.
You looked for him not knowing that?
If I had known, I would not have written the story.
You should know he is suspicious because of his mask, at least!
I do not know.
Love is blind!
Love?
That is right, Saitou worries about his position,
and cannot ever confess his love.
That just is not love!
What are you saying?
Get down!
Let us call for reinforcements!
They will not make it, take Ootsuka and run, Saitou!
I will hold him back!
Please do not be ridiculous!
I cannot abandon someone I lov
It is love!
That is all to it.
Saitou!
Saitou!
Li-kun?
Hei!
I found it, Hei!
W-What just happened?
Strangely, no one remembers what happened that night.
But it seems like it was not just me who did not feel clear about it,
the same feeling as if something is stuck in your throat.
Do not you remember, chief?
I am sure I remember saying something really important to you that night.
Sorry, I cannot remember.
Anyway, I feel that I found the truth regarding something very important.
However, only one thing was clear.
Ever since then, my allergies have been healed for some reason.
I do not know why, but I feel like I will have a nice spring.
Medicine for allergies?
Yeah, seems like it was made by the chemical department from the Gate.
If everything went well, it could have led to a complete cure.
So that is what that fluid was?
Yeah, but there is a negative side effect.
You lose a few days' worth of memory.
It is unfortunate, but it will be a while before it is put to use.
Wait, Huang, Hei and I have not lost our memories of that time.
Is it because of what Hei said then?
That contractors are not allergic to pollen.
Who knows?
I do not know about contractors.
Oh, it is the pink girl.
She is probably heading to Yin's place.
Hey, Huang.
We were able to collect the goods thanks to Yin remembering the number.
Yeah, do whatever you want.
Are not you glad, Yin?
Yeah.
It cannot be... right?
She is not coming today?
